The paper deals with document image analysis, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The focus of the paper is on feature extraction, which is a common task in information retrieval (cs.IR), deep learning (cs.DL), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions compression and efficiency, which are relevant topics in multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.LG, and cs.MM.
